心思想都唔錯<br />\n一直唔明自己肯做飯呢句有咩問題，覺得其實呢句野幾有意思幾鍾意呢句<br />\n但係佢嘅詞語法上真係錯撚晒<br />\n乜撚野牆壁舖滿了塵？牆壁點「舖」塵？明明牆壁同舖字都有其他同樣啱音但意思更好嘅字詞可以代表<br />\n如果佢肯努力下，俾D心機執下語法、騰多幾次、唔好尻填，其實都唔差嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42dcf9f9bcea350d4355e4c5037e99dba9230cb7","tid":1012805,"uid":194380,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:52:27.000Z","msg":"其實首詞講緊一個醉酒佬 一個醉咗既人做咩都好合理吖。所以謙謙係特登填到九唔搭八，好似飲醉咗咁。"},{"pid":"704d362bfe199054d338ab8e32c92d5a1f38c18b","tid":1012805,"uid":45208,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:23:28.000Z","msg":"你聽到一首廣東歌，唱的每一隻字你都懂得，但聽完又好似咩訊息都無接收到，係非常新奇的體驗。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n陳詠謙繼續J 番商台個填詞人大獎啦，力排眾議<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4a9e655d82ec3cc495a858b2a929427aef5e89","tid":1012805,"uid":232363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd459cddeac900ab8e3ba455c050a985a4f1d8ac","tid":1012805,"uid":129658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"42dcf9f9bcea350d4355e4c5037e99dba9230cb7","tid":1012805,"uid":194380,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:52:27.000Z","msg":"其實首詞講緊一個醉酒佬 一個醉咗既人做咩都好合理吖。所以謙謙係特登填到九唔搭八，好似飲醉咗咁。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:41:19.000Z","msg":"咁以後d歌寫個人發癲、就亂鳩咁填詞都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e635b0562a95b56551e7d56db29c2331cbd9fe5","tid":1012805,"uid":23247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:49:31.000Z